  "title": "Customer Service Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities: </strong></p><ul><li>Accurately inputting information into databases and spreadsheets.</li><li>Receiving and sorting incoming Order .</li><li>Issuing Credit / Debit Note .</li><li>Liaise with various team to fulfil customer’s order when needed .</li><li>Providing  timely and professional responses to customer inquiries .</li><li>Providing Timely Update of price list to existing clients </li><li>Filling / Sorting Supplier Invoice in running number .</li><li>Other  Ad-hoc job assigned by supervisors and/or managers .</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p><br /></p><ul><li>Proficient in MS Office (Words, Excel, Outlook)</li><li>At least 1 year or above related working experience in administrative duties      .</li><li>Good communication and inter-personal skills .</li><li>5.5-days per week</li></ul><p>Location     :  Tuas </p><p>Salary         :  $2700  - $3500</p><p>Company   :  Food Processing & Manufacturing Company </p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Lin Stephanie</p><p>EA Registration Number: R23118908</p><p>EA Licence No: 23C1729 ( SHR Global Talent )</p>",
